%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#ff4444', 'primaryTextColor': '#fff', 'primaryBorderColor': '#ff6666', 'lineColor': '#ff8888'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 👤 User
    participant CC as 🖥️ Claude Code
    participant SK as 🧠 Skill Engine
    participant HK as ⚡ Hook System
    participant AG as 🤖 Agent
    participant ST as 💾 State

    Note over U,ST: Skill Discovery & Trigger

    U->>CC: Input (slash command / keyword / task)
    CC->>HK: keyword-detector hook fires
    HK->>SK: Match trigger pattern

    alt Magic Keyword Match
        SK->>SK: Auto-detect skill from keyword table
        Note right of SK: "autopilot" → autopilot skill<br/>"ralph" → ralph skill<br/>"ulw" → ultrawork skill
    else Slash Command
        SK->>SK: Load skill by name
        Note right of SK: /plan → plan skill<br/>/team → team skill
    else Context Match
        SK->>SK: Skill description pattern match
    end

    Note over U,ST: Skill Loading & Execution

    SK->>CC: Inject skill content into context
    CC->>CC: Parse skill instructions
    CC->>ST: Write state (mode=active)

    loop Skill Execution Loop
        CC->>AG: Delegate to specialized agent(s)
        AG->>AG: Execute task
        AG-->>CC: Return results
        CC->>ST: Update progress
        CC->>HK: persistent-mode hook enforces continuation
    end

    Note over U,ST: Completion & Cleanup

    CC->>CC: Verify acceptance criteria
    CC->>ST: Clear state (mode=inactive)
    CC-->>U: Present results

    Note over U,ST: Auto-Learning Path

    rect rgb(39, 174, 96, 0.2)
        U->>CC: /learner — extract reusable skill
        CC->>SK: Generate new skill definition
        SK->>SK: Save to skills/ directory
        Note right of SK: Custom skills persist<br/>across sessions
    end
